      "body" : "@yancyribbens: It seems that your problem is caused by omitting any path name on executing `test_bitcoin`, which will search in `$PATH` for the binary, which then most likely is the installed one. To execute unit tests from your local build, either use `make check` or `src/test/test_bitcoin` (as described in `src/test/README.md`).",
